post_summaries.description: The image shows several pieces of vegan sushi arranged on a white plate. The sushi rolls have a dark purple/black seaweed wrap and are filled with pinkish-purple rice, a strip of avocado, and a piece of vegan salmon. The photo is taken at a close angle, highlighting the texture and colors of the sushi.

The image shows three plates of homemade vegan sushi. The sushi includes various fillings like carrots, tofu, avocado, and mushrooms. The post mentions the user now makes their own vegan sushi after being disappointed with store-bought options.

The image shows several platters of vegan sushi rolls. The caption mentions different types of rolls, including umami tofu, rainbow rolls, and teriyaki mushroom rolls. The post also mentions that this was a catering job for a concert in aid of a charity.

The image shows a homemade vegan sushi platter in a foil container. The sushi rolls contain ingredients like sweet potato, tofu, dill, yellow pepper, coriander, and carrot. There are also separate compartments with pickled ginger, wasabi, and what appears to be roasted red pepper.

The image shows a plate of vegan sushi. The caption lists three favorite vegan sushi combinations, including panko-crusted sweet potato with avocado and sriracha mayo, air-fried tofu with crunchy veg and topped with red pepper 'tuna', and teriyaki mushroom inside out roll with green beans, broccoli, black sesame and topped with coriander.
The image shows several plates of vegan sushi. There are different types of rolls, including inside-out rolls, and the caption mentions using tomato-based "vegan sashimi" as a topping.
